	   <tr><td colspan=2>Here is the deal all.<br>1) Any race with pure casters already has a robe model built into the game.&nbsp;&nbsp;If your race does not have any pure casters, this will not look like a robe on you.  That means that only human druids will look like they have robes on.<br>2) This IS a robe graphic, not a plate graphic.  It has nothing to do with plate at all AND iksars can wear it.<br>3) People ask why a tank would want it.  An SK or monk could get a little use out of it, but it is basically for show.<br><br>I'd like to finish by saying that contrary to popular belief, EQ is not all about stats.  Fashion, faction, and roleplaying are all factors that make the game enjoyable.  Imagine an Erudite Shadowknight in THIS robe wielding a Zealot's Incarnadine Sword or a Noctivigant Blade - it opens up whole new realms of roleplaying!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
